                            <comment id="16823012" author="ichattopadhyaya" created="Mon, 22 Apr 2019 10:49:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To summarise, when the prioritized overseer joined back (after a restart), all other nodes, one by one, became overseer leader and gave up leadership, until the prioritized overseer became the leader. During all this time, many overseer messages kept failing, perhaps due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13416&quot; title=&quot;Overseer node getting stuck&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-13416&quot;&gt;SOLR-13416&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
